>downshift from 3rd. It doesnt happen in any other gears only 2nd. It 
>usually wont go into 2nd until I rev the engine or complety slow down and 
>put it in 1st. Should I be really concerned about this or is it somewhat 
>normal. Thanks. Also my bus is a 72 westy with a 1700cc engine

